{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__2.gif?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/EvilPunk.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">EvilPunk is a VR shooter, base defense game set in a dark Western world. In this intense setting, you\u2019ll need to defend your hometown from an onslaught of demonic forces. Armed with a range of weapons and strategic skills, you\u2019ll face waves of enemies and prevent the Church from being sieged.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__1.gif?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Campaign_Mode.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Witness the story of Sheriff Salomon's fight against the demon army through his eyes. Become the world's last line of defense by using all the resources at your disposal. Each victory will take the relentless fight against the dark forces one step further, while each defeat will make you stronger.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__3.gif?t=1736437446\" />\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Boss_FIghts.png?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After fighting through waves of enemies, challenging boss fights await you at the end of each level. Each Boss has its own unique mechanics to discover. Discover them and use their weaknesses against them to achieve victory.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__4.gif?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Unique_Weapons.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While fighting different types of enemies, choose the weapon that suits your style to create the most effective strategies and protect your target: the Crystal and the Church. You need to plan carefully at every step to successfully maintain the defense of your base by applying the best tactics in difficult battles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__5.gif?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Shop_System.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your progress through the Waves depends on how you manage your resources. Kill the enemies you encounter and collect their drop. In between waves, buy supplies from the Shop with Silver Coins or continue the fight with a new weapon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__6.gif?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Weapon_UpGrade.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies will become stronger on each map, which will require constant upgrades and development of your weapons. As you pass the levels, you will be able to upgrade your weapons as you wish with the special coins you collect and have the opportunity to use them at their full power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/MicrosoftTeams-image__12_.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can join our Discord server to support our game, stay up to date on its development, and give us feedback!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Hard Way","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2968260/82f1a6ccced1d5aa4c55e8d8256c0fc02a6d6642.jpg"}],"total":1},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736437446","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/page.bg.jpg?t=1736437446","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/4eebea1157b95d5c187b68741b4d84fd3cb4e1f2/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736437446","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/4eebea1157b95d5c187b68741b4d84fd3cb4e1f2/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736437446","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"T