/></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your progress through the Waves depends on how you manage your resources. Kill the enemies you encounter and collect their drop. In between waves, buy supplies from the Shop with Silver Coins or continue the fight with a new weapon.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/GIF__6.gif?t=1736437446\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/Weapon_UpGrade.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enemies will become stronger on each map, which will require constant upgrades and development of your weapons. As you pass the levels, you will be able to upgrade your weapons as you wish with the special coins you collect and have the opportunity to use them at their full power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/extras/MicrosoftTeams-image__12_.png?t=1736437446\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can join our Discord server to support our game, stay up to date on its development, and give us feedback!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2>","developers":["Digivega Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968260/header.jpg?t=1736437446","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":25